<task id="UDSS-012" project="UI Dialog Shell Standardization">
  <metadata>
    <title>Extract CreateTodo wizard to shared library + Code Page wrapper</title>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <phase>2</phase>
    <estimated-effort>5 hours</estimated-effort>
    <tags>shared-library, wizard, todo, code-page, vite</tags>
    <dependencies>001, 002, 004</dependencies>
    <parallel-group>phase2-wizard-extraction</parallel-group>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Move the CreateTodo wizard (4 files) from LegalWorkspace inline components to the
    @spaarke/ui-components shared library, then create a standalone Vite Code Page wrapper.
    The CreateTodo wizard creates sprk_event records with todoflag=true. It shares structural
    similarity with CreateEvent but has distinct field mappings and validation logic.
  </prompt>

  <role>Frontend developer with expertise in React 19, Fluent UI v9, Vite, and Dataverse Code Pages</role>

  <goal>
    CreateTodo wizard lives in @spaarke/ui-components/components/CreateTodoWizard/ with 4 files,
    a new src/solutions/CreateTodoWizard/ Code Page exists and builds successfully via Vite,
    and the wizard can be opened from Corporate Workspace via navigateTo.
  </goal>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-012">Services must use IDataService abstraction — refactor todoService.ts to implement IDataService interface</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-026">Vite + vite-plugin-singlefile for Code Pages — single HTML output</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-021">Fluent v9 tokens only, React 19, dark mode support required</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-006">Standalone dialogs must be Code Pages, not PCF wrappers</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-012-shared-components.md</file>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-026-full-page-custom-page-standard.md</file>
      <file>.claude/patterns/webresource/full-page-custom-page.md</file>
      <file>src/solutions/LegalWorkspace/src/components/CreateTodo/</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step id="1">Move 4 files from LegalWorkspace/src/components/CreateTodo/ to src/client/shared/src/components/CreateTodoWizard/ — preserve all component logic including todoflag=true behavior</step>
    <step id="2">Refactor todoService.ts to implement IDataService abstraction — ensure sprk_event creation with todoflag=true is preserved</step>
    <step id="3">Export CreateTodoWizard from @spaarke/ui-components package index</step>
    <step id="4">Create src/solutions/CreateTodoWizard/ Code Page project with Vite config, viteSingleFile plugin, package.json, tsconfig.json</step>
    <step id="5">Create Code Page index.tsx that reads URL params (parentId, parentType), wraps wizard in FluentProvider + DialogShell</step>
    <step id="6">Run npm install and npm run build in both shared library and Code Page — fix any compilation errors</step>
    <step id="7">Verify single HTML file output exists in dist/ and is deployable as a Dataverse web resource</step>
  </steps>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion>4 wizard files exist in @spaarke/ui-components/components/CreateTodoWizard/</criterion>
    <criterion>todoService.ts implements IDataService interface</criterion>
    <criterion>CreateTodoWizard is exported from shared library package index</criterion>
    <criterion>src/solutions/CreateTodoWizard/ builds successfully with Vite producing a single HTML file</criterion>
    <criterion>Wizard correctly creates sprk_event records with todoflag=true</criterion>
    <criterion>No remaining CreateTodo component files in LegalWorkspace/src/components/</criterion>
    <criterion>npm run build succeeds with zero errors in both shared library and Code Page</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
